 WD, plays a\nkey role. Within the context of the hypothesized super-Chandrasekhar-mass WD\nscenario, we speculatively suggest a progenitor WD evolution including a\nspin-up accretion phase followed by a spin-down mass-ejection phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2023 01:23:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 02:48:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-08"}
