 the object classification task, the F1 score\nincreases from 0.8846 to 0.9230, and the accuracy score is up from 0.8375 to\n0.8875.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2023 02:51:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2023 08:29:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
