e the preparation of\nthe two-excitation Dicke state $|D^{4}_{2}\\rangle$ in a four-qubit system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2023 06:49:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Jun 2023 13:36:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-05"}
